          </table>
        </content>
      </paragraph>
      <paragraph>
        <content>
          <p><b>Transposition of </b>Commission Implementing Directive 2014/20/EU</p>
          <table uk:widths="1.55in 2.85in 2.01in">
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p><b>Article of Directive 2014/20/EU</b></p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p><b>Purpose</b></p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p><b>Implementation</b></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Article 1(a); point (1)(a) of Annex I (grade S)</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Seed potatoes marketed as “Union Grade S”.</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Reg. 4(1)(b) and (c); reg. 10(5); Schedule 4, Table 2.</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Point (1)(a)(i) of Annex I</p>
              </td>
              <td rowspan="6">
                <p>“Union Grade S” requirements.</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Schedule 4, Table 2 (Union Grade S), Column 3, point (a)(i).</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Point (1)(a)(ii) of Annex I</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Schedule 4, Table 2 (Union Grade S), Column 3, point (a)(iv)</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Point (1)(a)(iii) of Annex I</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Schedule 4, Table 2 (Union Grade S), Column 3, point (a)(v).</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Point (1)(a)(iv) of Annex I</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Schedule 4, Table 2 (Union Grade S), Column 3, point (a)(ii) and (iii) (standards are tighter in reliance of Article 5 of the principle Directive).</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Point (1)(a)(v) of Annex I</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Schedule 4, Table 2 (Union Grade S), Column 2.</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Point (1)(a)(vi) of Annex I</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Reg. 11(6)(b)(i).</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
